POLICY SERVER CODE REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------

1. Copy your part 2 policy server code to this directory
2. You may not use any non-standard C++ library except the rapidjson located at ../lib/rapidjson
3. Make sure your code can be compiled through a single `make` operation
4. Make sure your code can be cleaned through a single `make clean` operation
5. Make sure your policy server program is named AdvPolicyServer
6. Your policy server should not expect any command line arguments
7. Make sure your policy server program can be started through our run-policy-server.sh

Thanks!

